title: MisterMusic Show 369 - indie, alternative, rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 369 - [2 hours] 192kbps MP3

On this week's show new music by Boy & Bear, Foals, Emerald Park, and The Belligerents.
We travel back 32 years for the 'Oldie of the Week'. A song that was number 1 in the US,in early September 1983. It's a song that became the group's most recognizable tune.

The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on RockXS internet radio.
